cs.LG, cs.CR, cs.DC, cs.SI, cs.CY

This paper discusses distributed deep learning models that aim to protect confidential patterns in data while still allowing servers to train models. This topic is closely related to machine learning (cs.LG), as well as security and privacy (cs.CR) in distributed systems (cs.DC). Additionally, the paper discusses communication efficiency (cs.SI) and potential future trends (cs.CY) in this area. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG, followed by cs.CR, cs.DC, cs.SI, and cs.CY.
